Open the PowerShell terminal in administrator mode. 

Run zookeeper in Termianl 
.\bin\windows\zookeeper-server-start.bat .\config\zookeeper.properties


Again open the  second PowerShell terminal in administrator mode and run server. 
.\bin\windows\kafka-server-start.bat .\config\server.properties


Again open the PowerShell terminal in administrator mode and create the topic 
.\bin\windows\kafka-topics.bat --bootstrap-server 127.0.0.1:9092 --create --replication-factor 1 --partitions 1 --topic hashtags_topic 


Then press enter 
